    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-10-08T10:30:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-10-08T10:30:00-05:00" n="829"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d829">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 652.119/1916</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Curaçao</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Messersmith</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Willemstad</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-10-08T11:00:00-04:30">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 8, 1918, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received October 9, 6 p.m</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have the honor to transmit the following from Consul of the United States at
                    Puerto Cabello: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>October 7. Spanish steamer <hi rend="italic">Villamanrique</hi> desires
                            permission to proceed from here to Barcelona via Venezuelan ports and
                            port in the Canaries subject to same conditions as in original license
                            which reads Habana, Puerto Cabello, Barcelona, dated September 27.
                            Appears to be no objection to this change. Signed, <persName
                                corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_MHH1">Henry</persName>.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Send reply to Consul of the United States at Puerto Cabello.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Messersmith</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
